%% D-08 Message Send Flow — source: SPEC.md Appendix A
sequenceDiagram
  Client->>APIGateway: POST /messages
  APIGateway->>Identity: validate session
  APIGateway->>Authorisation: check permission
  APIGateway->>Messaging: persist message
  Messaging->>EventBus: MessagePosted
  EventBus->>RealTimeGateway: fanout
  EventBus->>Notification: notify
  EventBus->>Search: index
  EventBus->>Billing: meter
